Key Match Events: Sam Hauser made a game-winning three-pointer from the right corner in overtime after receiving a kick-out pass from Jayson Tatum with Boston trailing 91-89 with less than two minutes left in regulation.
Post-Match Reflections: Jayson Tatum expressed confidence in his teammates despite their shooting struggles, emphasizing the importance of maintaining faith in their abilities.
Al Horford maintained confidence by recalling the team's preparation and trusting their process after a poor shooting performance.
Joe Mazzulla praised the team's ability to empower and trust each other through tough shooting stretches.
